data.description:
Charming Bungelow 2 blocks away from UA campus! 2 bedrooms,2 full bathrooms and an office/den off of the kitchen. Original Wood floors & many original fixtures. Art deco heatilator w/ matching art deco sconces in the living room, Multiple built ins throughout home. Home also features a 560sq.ft. 2 car garage that would be great workshop or storage.PET POLICY: If approved: up to 2 pets, weight limit. $250 per pet non-refundable fee, pet rent $0 per pet/per month. Pet liability insurance required.DEPOSIT: $Equal to 1 month rent, Security deposit is OAC, additional deposit may be required.Northpoint Asset Management has partnered with Rhino to offer an affordable alternative to upfront cash security deposits. Additional $199 Non-refundable fee required. More information upon request. APPLICATION FEE: $69All persons residing in home or Co-signing, 18 years of age or older must apply. Link to application including pet screening: GET LINK FROM FINDIGS Only applications submitted through Findigs will be accepted and processed.NON-REFUNDABLE ADMIN FEE: $199 RESIDENT BENEFIT PACKAGE: All Northpoint Asset Management residents are enrolled in the Resident Benefits Package (RBP) for $50.00/month which includes renters insurance, HVAC air filter delivery and more. (contact Northpoint Leasing Agent for Details)RENTERS INSURANCE: Renters Insurance with $100,000 in liability is required. Coverage can be provided and is included with the Resident Benefit Package. Tenants have the option to obtain their own coverage.Listed and managed by Northpoint Asset Management **Equal Housing Opportunity**RENTAL CRITERIA:Verifiable Gross monthly income: $ 3 times rent Rental history: Good- evictions 7 yrs. or older or landlord collectionsGood Credit: Minimum score: 650 (AVE ONE is 580)Criminal Background: Per HUD Guidelines: Applicant is permitted to submit that information to management along with their application and Management will review that information on a case-by-case basis

Smoking allowed:No
